		<annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en-US">planned process that is prescribed by some recipe procedure</annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition>
		<annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageDefinition>every instance of &apos;recipe procedure occurrence&apos; is exactly an instance of &apos;recipe procedural element occurrence&apos; that &apos;is prescribed by&apos; some &apos;recipe procedure&apos;</annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageDefinition>
		<annotation:usageNote>This class is intended to be a defined class used for axiomatization and assertion convenience. It is not expected nor recommended that entities will be asserted directly as a subclass or instance of this class.</annotation:usageNote>
	</owl:Class>
	
